column5: What are the main access points to Rock Lake? I know on the NE corner theres a beach there which I think is access, and theres a chunk of crown on the SW side too. Are there any other access areas I'm missing?  Thanks!
i don't know what the road is called, but it puts you out on the lake right near the rivermouth.

shhhhh archie!! i drove my truck right to the beach not to long ago, they dont have much snow out that way. a sled will do you wonders for getting you where you wanna go out there, if not then i say just go to ottertail, gordon, or carbiou. good luck out there
